        "text_GKxgpW": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Hugbel provides specification-grade lighting designed for reliable performance in residential and light commercial projects.<br/><br/>Our fixtures are engineered with accurate voltage compatibility (110–120V / 220–240V), proper driver selection, and certified components that meet global standards including UL, CE, RoHS, and AS/NZS.</p><p>We work directly with specialized manufacturers to ensure consistent lumen <br/>output, stable color temperature, safe thermal management, and long-term electrical reliability.</p><p>From pendant lights to chandeliers, our collection blends style with safety. We also offer customization to bring your vision to life—perfect for any project, big or small.</p>",
